::Shadow Wing::

She laughed."Oh really? We'll see about that!" She flew off after him. 
Weaving in and out of trees, with a smirk on her face and determinded to tag 
him back.  "I'll get you yet." she said with a chuckle in her voice. She 
felt the owl in her self start to fly again. She had a smile on her face and 
the wind under her wings.  She saw him running along just ahead of her.  He 
looked happy and free.  He was like a puppy again.  Running with the wind in 
his face and his tongue hanging out.  She laughed. He looked happy to just 
be running again. Without worry or care, just having fun again.  She flew 
after him and came up behind him.
"I'm going to catch you."

"I'd like that," Was Lunarpines response,"Better yet, how about a
game of tag,I haven't tracked airborne prey in a long time."
Lunarpine was anxious for a challenge, and a little fun.

"Oh by the way, "YOU'RE IT" he reached up and gave Shadow Wing a
smack, as he transformed to Wolf mode and ran off. (What part of
Africa are we in?)
